<li><p><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yPIvqJsCOSo" id="_r1MzmyyI" data-link-icon="youtube" data-link-icon-type="svg" data-link-icon-color="#ff0033">Bitcoin: The New Gold Standard</a></p></li>
<li><p><a href="https://blockonomi.com/sound-money-bitcoin/" id="_jhZ93FYt">What is Sound Money? A Look at Bitcoin’s Emergence</a></p></li>
